Laparoscopic versus open inguinal herniorrhaphy: preliminary results of a 
randomized controlled trial.

Barkun JS(1), Wexler MJ, Hinchey EJ, Thibeault D, Meakins JL.

Author information:
(1)Divisions of General Surgery, Royal Victoria Hospital, Montreal, Quebec, 
