BACKGROUND: Benefits of laparoscopic herniorrhaphy (LH) over open hernia repair 
(OH) remain unproved.
METHODS: Interim analysis of a prospective randomized controlled trial compared 
OH with LH where study outcomes were measured by third-party evaluators through 
